title: Begin drive for memes and official memes twitter
body:
For a long time now, memes have been known to be great devices for getting messages and information out to people. Memes that are associated with token projects have been very effective at increasing interest in the token, as well as, attracting more people to the community that surrounds the token.

Unfortunately, for the KIMCH token, there has been a relative lack of good, original memes.

One of the goals of this proposal is to spur the creation of more original KIMCHI memes by the community. 

By filling that lack of memes, we should expect to reap the benefits that memes can provide. Just as so many other projects have done and are doing.

The first step in this process is to begin creating KIMCHI memes and posting them in the "memes" channel on the KimchiDAO Discord.

After we have begun to create more memes, we can curate them and post the best ones on an official Kimchi Memes Twitter. Then community members can retweet them to expose the Kimchi project to an even greater audience.

Proposal: 

Begin a drive for creating original Kimchi memes for publication on an official Kimchi Memes Twitter
choices: No, do not pursue memes campaign
